{"tid":1863404,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【第貳拾肆期牆紙】 疫戰","createTime":"2020-02-05T06:34:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-12T01:32:52.000Z","uid":253119,"like":20,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"024d31e76494add4c78cc97d6080af494ccd5dd7","tid":1863404,"uid":253119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T06:34:46.000Z","msg":"第一宗武漢肺炎死亡個案已經發生，當香港人的生命受著巨大威脅，因著政府的不作為，醫護除了在第一線以身犯險，更被逼代替政府保障香港的公共衛生&mdash;&mdash;爭取封關。然而，卻只換來林鄭批評為「極端手段」。當某些人一直只求安穩時，任由政府獨裁的後果終於浮現，由你和我一起承受。<br />\n<br />\n今期《牆紙》有幸訪問了數位護士，談談他們對此次疫情的看法，及和大家回顧一下沙士時期。盼望在此次逆境，香港人再次𢹂手面對，對抗這洶湧的疫情、這視市民如草芥的暴政。<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n目錄<br />\n 1. 沙士回憶<br />\n 2. 一罩難求<br />\n 3. 能獨善其身的，是你嗎？<br />\n 4. 討賣港賊檄<br />\n 5. 社會契約、道德哲學、醫護罷工 - 授權刊登<br />\n 6. 醫護界護士訪問<br />\n 7. 魚革投稿<br />\n 8. 台灣大選賽後點評總統篇<br />\n 9. 台灣大選賽後點評立委篇<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n點擊連結用投稿衝擊牆紙：@wallpaperneedyou<br />\n<br />\n#24期 #24th<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZhwYykd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZhwYykd.jpg&h=2798385d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uDs8Vyz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuDs8Vyz.jpg&h=52a16549&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H43cCMV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH43cCMV.jpg&h=83066cd9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WkbxCMW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWkbxCMW.jpg&h=7b795375&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YX6Q8TC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYX6Q8TC.jpg&h=3ec6e2a1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u5ZnZ0h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu5ZnZ